[SN]TITLE[SN]
Drumsurn: Controlled explosion on viable device

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A controlled explosion has been carried out on a viable device in Drumsurn near Limavady.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police say the security operation is continuing.
Earlier, a number of people who had to leave their homes returned to their houses.
It was reported on Wednesday that a bomb had been left in the area. There was a police presence in the area on Friday.
An anonymous telephone call was passed to police on Wednesday to say a device had been left at Legavallon Road.
Part of the road has been closed to traffic and diversions are in place.
